Phrase: From the base, we drove the Mist Train to the POI indicated on the map by Islington and Yoshino.
Barriers have been restored around the station where we are based, but there is no protection here. The area is crawling with Monsters living in the Sea of Fog.

Name: Queensway
Phrase: There is a tremendous amount of enemies. Though, we're in the Sea of Fog, so it's not surprising I think.

Name: Vivienne
Phrase: Whoever got inside that Portal... I don't know how she's holding up so well on her own. I hope it's safer than outside...

Name: Finchley
Phrase: Unfortunately that doesn't seem to be the case. I'd rather think it's more dangerous inside.

Name: Queensway
Phrase: Instructor Finchley!

Name: Finchley
Phrase: Queensway, you've improved a lot in the little time I've seen you. I can tell by your expression and your behaviour. Well, I suppose you've been through so many ordeals, you must have gone stronger.

Name: Queensway
Phrase: Thank you very much! I owe it all to the guidance of Instructor Finchley.

Name: Queensway
Phrase: If Instructor Finchley is here, does that mean that you are still participating in the mission as an Out-Sider?

Name: Finchley
Phrase: Yes, I was approached directly by my commanding officer. I was here to watch the door until I could join you.

Name: Putra
Phrase: That's the Instructor Finchley we know. I can't believe you're alone in a dangerous place like this.

Name: Finchley
Phrase: No way. Even I wouldn't defend a place like this by myself. I wouldn't be able to alert anyone if something happened to me.

Name: Vivienne
Phrase: Meaning you've got company.'

Name: Finchley
Phrase: Yes, there are three of us excluding me.'

Name: Yakutsk
Phrase: Three... I can't detect any one of them at all. So you all are pretty good at concealment.

Name: Finchley
Phrase: The only reason they're not detected is because I've been on guard here all night. They're not hiding from you guys though.

Name: Fayette
Phrase: That's right. I wasn't hiding to scare ya'll.

Name: Ohana
Phrase: Oh dear, Fayette-san, you mustn't lie. Just a moment ago, you were looking for the right moment to jump out from behind Yakutsk-san's back.

Name: Yakutsk
Phrase: Fayette. And Ohana too.

Name: Fayette
Phrase: Hey there, it's been awhile. Yakutsk. Thanks for looking after me at Loren Citadel.

Name: Yakutsk
Phrase: We're the ones who were indebted to you. My sister Bestyakh also thanked you and Detroit.

Name: Putra
Phrase: Hey, why is Ohana here...?

Name: Vivienne
Phrase: That's what I thought too. Mademoiselle Ohana was supposed to be at the base, wasn't she?

Name: Ohana
Phrase: That's because I joined up with them later, just like everyone else. I wasn't on guard here all night.

Name: Putra
Phrase: No, that's not what I meant.

Name: Vivienne
Phrase: Okay, Putra. Keep it up. Don't let that smile brush over you.

Name: Putra
Phrase: I'll take care of it! I'm going to give her a good talking-to! I'm not a half-hearted straight man either, you know. I'm not going to let Queensway get the better of me.

Name: Vivienne
Phrase: Okay, Ohana vs Putra. Ready... fight!

Name: Putra
Phrase: I have one word for you, Miss Ohana!

Name: Ohana
Phrase: Hmmhmm~. It's great to be young. Being rowdy's good~

Name: Putra
Phrase: I'll say it! I'm going to point out something funny about you, Ohana!

Name: Vivienne
Phrase: Say it! Tell her, Putra!

Name: Putra
Phrase: Ohana was acting suspiciously with the Tsukiyo Banshuu at the base just now, so how are you farther ahead than us!? We just came here on the Mist Train!

Name: Putra
Phrase: Besides, the strong-looking Tsukiyo Banshuu were really perky, weren't they? Ohana, perhaps you all are doing all sorts of things behind the scenes!

Name: Ohana
Phrase: Ah, I see~

Name: Ohana
Phrase: ...So, what were you talking about?

Name: Putra
Phrase: What the heck? All you did was just to say 'I see' for a second! At least come up with a better excuse to shrug this off!

Name: Finchley
Phrase: Putra, leave it. You can't keep messing around like this.

Name: Finchley
Phrase: There's nothing suspicious about Miss Ohana!

Name: Putra
Phrase: No, nobody said she was suspicious.

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: Ohana came here to help the Tsukiyo Banshuu. Whereas Finchley Kyoukan and Fayette are working for the Out-Siders.

Name: Yakutsk
Phrase: So when Islington mentioned to us about the officer of the Out-Siders, she was referring about Finchley? That's not quite what I was expecting.

Name: Finchley
Phrase: Blimey, Yakutsk. Are you saying I'm not good enough for you?

Name: Yakutsk
Phrase: No, T-that's not what I meant! Queensway was really surprised when she heard that an officer of the Out-Siders was going to join the fight, so...

Name: Putra
Phrase: Her reaction was that someone really scary was coming. I mean, Finchley is a scary enough person, but...

Name: Paddington
Phrase: The Out-Siders are famous for its extremely small number of officers. It's made up entirely of graduates and enlisted individuals, as we call them in the army. It has a special rank system whereby officers are not promoted unless they have proven themselves.

Name: Paddington
Phrase: Anyone who wants to get ahead should not join the Out-Siders. The Out-Siders wants three things: strength, victory and challenge!

Name: Paddington
Phrase: To be recognised as an officer of the Out-Siders, you must have exceptional fighting ability and mental strength. Then there's the ability to lead a team of fierce fighters!

Name: Fayette
Phrase: Well, you sure know your way around. Did Islington teach you?

Name: Paddington
Phrase: 'Yes! My sister taught me when I was a child that I might one day be in command of the Out-Siders! Unfortunately, that day is unlikely to come when I grow up!

Name: Fayette
Phrase: You make no sign or sound of footsteps when moving though. As expected of the Elrond family's Divine Children. You have potential.

Name: Queensway
Phrase: Well, I'm very grateful to be accompanied by Instructor Finchley, who is very reliable...

Name: Queensway
Phrase: Instructor Finchley is not an officer of the Out-Siders, are you? As I recall, I don't think your rank had changed since your time on active service as an Out-Sider.

Name: Finchley
Phrase: Yeah, your memories are correct. I'm not an officer, merely a non-comissioned officer.

Name: Queensway
Phrase: Do you have any plans to become an officer in the near future?

Name: Finchley
Phrase: No way. The Out-Siders aren't so naive as to think that someone who has left the front line before can command a unit.

Name: Finchley
Phrase: And I'm not even close to be an Out-Siders officer in terms of my ability.

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: Which means the last one who hasn't shown up yet is a strong person, an officer. And sHe said there were three other people besides Finchley Kyoukan.

Name: Ohana
Phrase: Yes, she is very strong and reliable girl~

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: Oh, even Ohana admits that she is strong. This looks very promising.

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: At least enough to get a hold of Finchley Kyoukan by the scruff of her neck.

Name: Blackfriar
Phrase: That's riiight, I'm an individual strong enough to hold Finchley by the scruff of her neck~♪

Name: Finchley
Phrase: Ouargh!
That is exactly what happened, without a sound or a sign. The figure suddenly appeared from behind Finchley.
By the time Yoshino caught sight of her, Finchley's body is already in the air.

Name: Blackfriar
Phrase: Hello. Members of the SSS... I'm Blackfriar, who's going to join you all on this mission. I'm in charge as the Out-Siders's training unit.

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: Train-ing u-nit?

Name: Fayette
Phrase: It is the unit responsible for the training and development of Out-Sider members. Instructor Blackfriar is in charge there.

Name: Queensway
Phrase: So the officer of the Out-Siders is Miss Blackfriar.

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: Oh, You're in charge of a Kyorentai, which means you're a Kyoren specialist.

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: You're, a Spanking officer!

Name: Blackfriar
Phrase: Fayette? If you've got time to waste, why don't you go and check on the Portal? Isn't it almost time for your regularly scheduled routine?

Name: Fayette
Phrase: Y-Yes! Right away!

Name: Fayette
Phrase: Let's go, Yakutsk! Come here! Come!

Name: Yakutsk
Phrase: What!? Why me! You haven't even explained anything to me yet!

Name: Fayette
Phrase: I'll explain it over there!

Name: Blackfriar
Phrase: 'Aha, you went in pairs, as per regulations. That's Fayette for you.

Name: Blackfriar
Phrase: Yes, that's why Blackfriar, the 'Spanking Officer', is also going with you all to look for the Giant Tree Route Map. I'll only be strict with my direct subordinates, so don't worry~.

Name: Finchley
Phrase: Um, I'm not supposed to be your direct subordinate at the moment...

Name: Blackfriar
Phrase: 'What? Even if you're not my subordinate, you're still my junior, right? If you're been my junior since knighthood school, you're junior to me for the rest of your life, until the day you die, am I right?

Name: Finchley
Phrase: It-It's an honour!

Name: Blackfriar
Phrase: Therefore, there's no problem! I give special treatment to cute juniors, that's my style~♪
